// Element assignment on a [float] list. Earlier the QBE backend
// passed a `d` (double) temp where mix_list_set expects an `l`,
// causing an ICE. Both backends should now bit-cast the double
// before storing.
main()
    xs! = [1.0, 2.0, 3.0]
    xs![0] = 0.5
    xs![1] = 9.5
    xs![2] = 100.25
    print(xs[0])
    print(xs[1])
    print(xs[2])

    ns! = [10, 20, 30]
    ns![1] = 999
    print(ns[0])
    print(ns[1])
    print(ns[2])
